data.description: Price Drop Alert: Now $485,000! Total Price Reduction is $48,000!! Experience modern luxury in South-Crest Estates, Lubbock. This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath home in a cul-de-sac showcases a modern architectural design. From the striking walkway to the impressive double doors, this home wows from the first glance. Inside, the open-plan living area, kitchen, and dining room soar with 12 ft. ceilings. The kitchen dazzles with quartz countertops, a side-by-side refrigerator, and stainless appliances - perfect for entertaining. Bedrooms feature 10ft ceilings and spacious walk-in closets. The expansive master suite boasts a large closet, a private patio, and access to a backyard with a built-in BBQ grill. Added perks include a large laundry room with freezer space and a convenient mudroom by the garage. Welcome to your dream home!
